178
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,550
Đau.

179
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,150
Nhưng mà

180
00:12:51,150 --> 00:12:53,270
tôi vẫn mong Cố Tầm

181
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:55,790
